Wizard Ghost: My dear mortal, let us begin most important lesson of all!
Wizard Ghost: Today, I will be introducing you to... necromancy!
Wizard Ghost: To be completely honest with you, er... I have never successfully performed the necromancy ritual.
Wizard Ghost: But I know the process, and will teach it to you! First, think of your past life, and one thing you truly loved about it.
